    AutoComplete<T,java.lang.String>, Input<java.lang.String>, ItemInput<T>, LengthInput<java.lang.String>, OptionalInput, ParseInput<java.lang.String>

    public abstract class AutocompleteTextInput<T>
extends TextInput
implements ItemInput<T>, AutoComplete<T,java.lang.String>
    A TextInput with an auto-complete list. This may also be displayed as a text-box plus pull-down. It is an ItemInput to allow the suggestions to show expanded selection text but it it possible to set String values that don't correspond to an Item.

    James
